Khumar Episode 11 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 29th December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

Director: Ali Faizan

Paane Ke Koshish Mei Hai Peeche Saara Zamaana,
Guzroo Yaha Se Jo Main
Ho Jaye Na HungamaтАж
Aashique Hai Saare Mere Karte Rahe Bahana тАж.
Chor Denge Chor Denge Hum 
Has Ke Yun Chor Denge HumтАж
Dhin Tak Dhin Tak Dhin
Nacha Ke Dikha Denge Hum тАж

Latka Dikha Diya Humne,
Jhatka Laga Hai Kyu Tumko ?
Tada тАж O Tumko TadaтАж. 
Matka Ke Chal Diye Hum Jo 
Khatka Hua Hai Kyu Tum Ko ?
Tada тАж O Tumko Tada тАж..

Hey Senorita 
Teri Kitni Kara Main Tareefa ?
Sunn Bonita 
Aise Door Na Ja , Kareeb AaaтАж..

Main Toh Deewana Tera,
Sun Le Fasana MeraтАж 
Tere Liye Maine Chora Hai Sabko
Yun Toh Na Dil Ko DukhaтАж

Tod Denge Tod Denge Hum, 
Jo Hai Yeh Tere Bharam,
Rule Kare Jag Saara 
Aur Hum Hi Kare Hai Run тАж.. 

Latka Dikha Diya Tune
Jhatka Laga Hai Yun Dil Ko 
Tada O Tumko TadaтАж
Matka Ke Chal Diye Tu Jo
Atka Hua Hai Dil Yeh Toh
Tada O Tumko TadaтАж.

Karti Hu Guroor
Tujhko Main Yeh Du BataтАж
Deewane Door Ja 
Na Mujhko Tu Yun SataтАж.

Main Woh Aatish Jo Jala Du ,
Bekhayali Ka Sama HuтАж
Jo Na Utre Woh Nasha HuтАж
Main Woh Raaj Ek Gehra HuтАж..
Jo Mita De Woh Bala Hu .. 
Main Toh Sab Ki Tamanna Hu тАж 

Teri Neendein Uda DuтАж..
Teri Shamein Saja DuтАж..

Jhatka Laga Hai Yun Dil Ko 
Tada O Tumko TadaтАж

Atka Hua Hai Dil Yeh Toh
Tada O Tumko TadaтАж.

Tada тАж O Tumko TadaтАж. 
Matka Ke Chal Diye Hum Jo 
Khatka Hua Hai Kyu Tum Ko ?
Tada тАж O Tumko Tada тАж..

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3965: Meeting Ka Reason
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jethalal notices Bhide has not arrived at the clubhouse, he inquires Taarak about his whereabouts. Taarak assures Jetha that he is not cognizant of Bhide. The residents of Gokuldham gradually arrive, but Bhide is nowhere to be found. Jetha and the other members are curious about the cause of Bhide's meeting. Finally, Madhavi and Bhide come, but they inform everyone that it was Tapu Sena who asked for the rendezvous.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Baylagaam Mega Ep 91 - [Eng Sub] Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 28th Dec 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

Written By: Huma Hina Nafees
Directed By: Zahid Mehmood

I feel if you are in your mid thirties or forties this video is specially important as we are working professionals due to our work and lifestyle ignore our health, which is one of them most important thing.

Looking for ways to flaunt the healthy skin of your dreams this festive season? In todayтАЩs video, IтАЩm going to reveal how to achieve spotless, bright skin in three simple steps by using GarnierтАпvitamin CтАпskincare products. So, without further ado, letтАЩs get started. 

Vitamin C, being one of the most effective ingredients in the skincare industry, offers a variety of benefits to the skin. And to make the most of this ingredient, itтАЩs crucial to include it in your skincare routine, be it as a cleanser, serum, moisturiser or more, especially when the festive season is here. So, to help you flaunt spotless, bright skin and prep it for the festive season, hereтАЩs a simple yet super effective 3-step skincare regimen to cleanse, treat and seal moisture in your skin effortlessly тАУ 

Step 1: Start by cleansing your face with theтАпGarnier Bright Complete Face Wash to get rid of dirt, dust, oil, sebum, and impurities. Apply the face wash on wet face and massage gently, avoiding the eye contour area. TheтАпvitamin C face washтАпhelps reduce dullness and restore your glowing, healthy-looking complexion. It also helps lessen dark spots and acne marks in just a few days, while leaving the skin feel bright. TheтАпGarnier Vitamin C face washтАпis gentle on the skin and suitable for all skin types. 

Step 2: Next, using the dropper take out a pea-sized amount of theтАпGarnier Vitamin C Serum and apply it on cleansed skin. Dab theтАпGarnier face serumтАпall over your face and neck using small, gentle tapping motions. Enriched with 30XтАпvitamin C, the Garnier serum fades dark spots and dull skin in just three days. It is made with a combination ofтАпvitamin C, niacinamide and salicylic acid to give your skin an instant boost of freshness and brightness. The lightweight and non-oily formula instantly penetrates the skin and makes it feel super comfortable all day long. TheтАпvitamin C face serumтАпis available in four different sizes for you to choose from and is formulated without sulphates and parabens. 

Step 3: Finish off your three-stepтАпvitamin CтАпroutine by applyingтАпthe Garnier Bright Complete Serum CreamтАпevenly on your face and neck. TheтАпGarnier Serum CreamтАпis made with a two-in-one formulation that helps you achieve the best of both worlds. It easily penetrates the deepest level of the skin and shields it from signs of sun damage such as skin tanning, dark spots, and sunburn. This cream also lightens dark spots, brightens skin, and evens skin tone. 

These products are definitely a game-changer for me. Highly recommended! So, what are you waiting for? Grab your hands on the GarnierтАпvitamin CтАпskincare products right away toтАп#CleanseTreatSealтАпyour skin on the go this festive season. 

I hope you found this video helpful and if you did, donтАЩt forget to like, share, and subscribe to my channel for more such videos. Also, let me know your thoughts in the comments below.тАп 
Thank you for watching, see you soon!
